text.tspan: Need clarification by the Dans here, the logic should be the same as ipv4 tho
Single click adds an IPv4 address, click and hold opens a dropdown which allow to choose IPv6
OS X uses this disposition, I think it makes more sense
Alternativelly we can use a modal dialog to ask what to add on click.
Automatic should be something like DHCP then Link-local,
Automatic are there only if automatic methods are
Each type of automatic can be added just once, so if already there the method combobox became
a label set to manual. In manual the user can set an IPv4 or an IPv6 address.
*The IPv4 combobox is there just as an example it should be a label since all possible options are there already
If changing the combobox in a label is problematic we can keep the combobox with the dropdown
